[ Pan only - thin steaks, < 1" ]
- heat pan to 200C
- cook until visible from the side
- flip, cook roughly the same again

[ Reverse-sear - thicker steaks, > 1" ]
- Preheat oven to 120C - 135C
- Heat pan to 200C (a bit later)
- Cook in oven until internal temp is 49C - 52C (for med-rare)
- Sear steak in hot pan to get crust
